Use:
import pygtk_baloon
pygtk_baloon.baloon(title,message,timeout,position)

-------------------------
Timeout is in ms.
Position:
1 = Up Left
2 = Up Right
3 = Bottom left
4 = Bottom right
5 = Bottom left (Fixed Win32)
6 = Bottom right (Fixed Win32)

-------------------------
Example:
import pygtk_baloon
pygtk_baloon.baloon("Try Title","Hello!!!", 10000, 4)
